Nutritional support and efficient gastroduodenal endoscopy in the treatment of acute pancreatitis and different forms of pancreonecrosis. Nutrition support and molecular-genetic markers of the immune system at patients with complicated forms of gastric pathology. In this study presented results of surgery clinic of and oncology faculty SGMU to improve treatment patients with acute pancreatitis, and various forms of pancreonecrozis, through a balanced Threpsology support and operational gastrointestinal endoscopy.